<br>
Yeah I wonder why your tranquil staff taunts more =P. Heh, I'll be working on getting one of those waay later in the game.<br>
<br>
Right now, I'm thinking about aiming towards a Jade mace and a Stave of Sheilding...this will be a long term project since the combine sum of the two will be around 22k. Which to me is still a crap load of pp. Anywho. Thanks for the info everyone I deeply appreciate it =)<br>
